        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>The way we choose engagement rings is changing, and 2025 is the year individuality and conscious luxury take center stage. From <em>lab-grown diamonds</em> to personalized designs that tell a story, today’s couples are redefining what forever means.</p><p>India, known for its love of timeless jewelry, is now embracing modern, ethical choices and Lucira Jewelry is leading the movement with elegant, sustainable designs crafted for the modern Indian couple.</p>",
            "custom_id": "",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "The Rise of Ethical Elegance: Conscious Luxury",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>The Rise of Ethical Elegance: Conscious Luxury</h2><p>More couples are saying “yes” to diamonds that shine responsibly. The rise of lab-grown diamond jewelry is transforming how people view luxury. These diamonds are physically and chemically identical to mined stones but they come without the environmental cost.</p><p>Lucira Jewelry’s collection reflects this evolution. Every ring is made with IGI-certified, conflict-free diamonds that radiate brilliance while supporting sustainability. Whether you’re exploring<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/1-carat-lab-grown-diamond-price-in-india\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">1 carat lab grown diamond price in India</span></a> or looking for bespoke engagement ring styles, Lucira brings conscious craftsmanship to every design.</p>",
            "custom_id": "the-rise",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Top Engagement Ring Trends 2025",
          "settings": {
