        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Trending Engagement Ring Styles in India",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Trending Engagement Ring Styles in India</h2><p>India’s jewelry landscape blends tradition and innovation beautifully.<br/> While northern regions favor sleek and modern platinum designs, the south often embraces rich gold tones and intricate motifs. Across the country, couples are now choosing lab-grown diamonds as a sustainable and affordable alternative.</p><p>Lucira’s modern selection includes everything from classic solitaires to contemporary bands, making it easy to find your dream ring. Their expertise extends beyond rings explore matching<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-earrings\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond earrings</span></a> or a<a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/collections/lab-grown-diamond-necklace\"> <span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">lab grown diamond necklace</span></a> to complete your bridal ensemble.</p>",
            "custom_id": "trending",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "How to Choose Your Perfect Engagement Ring",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>How to Choose Your Perfect Engagement Ring</h2><p>Finding the right engagement ring involves more than just sparkle. Here are a few essentials to consider:</p><ul><li>Lifestyle: Choose a design that suits your daily wear minimal styles for active lifestyles or bold ones for statement lovers.<br/></li><li>Diamond Cut: Shapes like round, oval, and cushion remain timeless favorites.<br/></li><li>Metal Type: Platinum and rose gold are trending for their elegance and durability.<br/></li><li>Ethical Choice: Opt for lab-grown diamonds to support sustainability without compromising brilliance.<br/></li></ul><p>Lucira Jewelry makes it easy to explore certified, conflict-free designs with transparent pricing and expert guidance.</p>",
            "custom_id": "how",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ADDTPa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion: Redefine Forever with Lucira Jewelry",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion: Redefine Forever with Lucira Jewelry</h2><p>The engagement ring trends of 2025 reflect a beautiful shift from convention to creativity, from mined to mindful. As modern couples look for pieces that embody love and values, <a href=\"https://www.lucirajewelry.com/\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Lucira Jewelry</span></a> stands out as India’s go-to destination for ethical brilliance and modern elegance.</p><p>Ready to find your forever ring?<br/> Explore Lucira’s collection of lab-grown diamond engagement rings, crafted to shine as brightly as your love.</p>",
            "custom_id": "conclusion",
            "text_alignment": "left"
          }
